Package: sRtr
Title: Tools for Working with UNOS SRTR Transplant Data in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Vagish", "Hemmige", email = "vahemmig@montefiore.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
  Provides functions and infrastructure to support reproducible research 
  using the United Network for Organ Sharing (UNOS) Scientific Registry of 
  Transplant Recipients (SRTR) data. The package facilitates standardized 
  data loading, cleaning, labeling, and analysis workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en
